snippet.textDisplay:
Dear Star Wars Theory,
I wanted to say I enjoyed Vader episode 1, and appreciate you and your channel. Especially in this time of not just political but also fan division, you stay respectful and drama-free. You do voice your opinion, but you do so I'd say, with grace. Not to offend, not to attack, but to state it.
I'd also like to say while I'd love to see further episodes of Vader come out, I am one fan that would prefer you to buy your own house and put down some roots.
And I guess you're thinking ahead, while watching your video, I was thinking maybe you should after Vader write your own films to make, ones that you can kick start and profit from. Heck, you've already got a fan base, many of us would take an interest. But it looks like you've got that idea bouncing around already.
You've got a good head on your shoulders. Hope you do well with everything (especially with buying the house and your personal life).
snippet.textOriginal:

I'd also like to say while I'd love to see further episodes of Vader come out, I am one fan that would prefer you to buy your own house and put down some roots.

Heck, you've already got a fan base, many of us would take an interest. But it looks like you've got that idea bouncing around already.
You've got a good head on your shoulders. Hope you do well with everything (especially with buying the house and your personal life).
